# FRED economic time series
# series_id is the FRED identifier, kind becomes the fact kind
series_id  kind  every
DFF        federal_funds_rate  6h
CPIAUCSL   cpi  24h
UNRATE     unemployment  24h
MORTGAGE30US  mortgage_30yr  24h
HOUST      housing_starts  24h
T10Y2Y     yield_curve_10y2y  6h
GDP        gdp  24h
